channel.title: New Highscores Theme, Orange Abstract (OFFICIAL RELEASE)
channel.description:
I've created yet another theme for highscores, this one was done by popular demand from a few people on my other post, its an orange abstract theme and i'm releasing it to you, This one has taken me about two hours to finish, making sure that everything looks right, the buttons on the page get brighter when you hover over them, creating a nice effect. All you need to do is drag all of the contents from the '.rar' file that you can download below directly to your highscores root directory, where you see, 'RS_Styles.css' and other files like that. Below is an image for the theme aswell as a link to my other blue abstract theme that i have created. Also, This theme was created with the, 'OrangeFox' SMF Forum theme in mind, by demand, it matches fairly good aswell.
[IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/lglty.png[/img]
[center][size=36pt][u][b]Download[/b][/u][/size] [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?jyarrve14n8zefy]Mediafire (.rar)[/url][/center]
[center][size=36pt][u][b]Other Theme(s)[/b][/u][/size] [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,537548.0.html]New Highscores Theme, Blue Mystic Look (OFFICIAL RELEASE)[/url]
